humshakals ( english : look-alikes ) is a 2014 indian romantic comedy film directed by sajid khan and produced by vashu bhagnani .   saif ali khan , ram kapoor and riteish deshmukh are in triple roles .   the film is shot extensively in foreign locations , starting september 2013 .   the film is co-produced by fox star studios and vashu bhagnani 's pooja entertainment .   the film was released on 20 june 2014 .   the film was heavily panned upon its release .   individuals starring in the movie and otherwise associated with it such as bipasha basu and esha gupta also criticized its production publicly .   regarded as one of the worst films ever made in indian history , the movie also failed to make back its production costs in the box office .